About this document

This document was generated using RMarkdown, and the source is available on Gitlab at: https://gitlab.com/fmichonneau/carpentrycon2018-tweets.

Pull requests to add other figures or fix bugs are welcome.

This document (and associated code) is released under a CC0 licence.

If you have questions or comments, I am on twitter at fmic_ or by email at francois.michonneau@gmail.com
